Retrieve operation of resource: summary

interface-list-name: string
in path

ID of interface-list-name

200 OK
summary_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK) 
{
  
"summary": {Summary information

    
"interface": [No description

      {
        
"not-supported-replications": "integer", Number of replications failed because\nunsupported

        
"pending-replications": "integer", Number of pending replications

        
"is-fib-downloaded": "boolean", Is interface downloaded to FIB

        
"interface-name": "string" Interface name

      }
    ],
    
"interface-list-name-xr": "string", Interface-list name

    
"number-of-interfaces": "integer", Number of interfaces

    
"interface-list-id": "integer" Interface internal ID

  }
}

BRIDGE-DOMAIN - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-l2vpn-oper:l2vpnv2/active/bridge-domains/bridge-domain/{bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name}/

Retrieve operation of resource: bridge-domain

bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name: string
in path

ID of bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name

200 OK
bridge-domain_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)

BRIDGE-ACCESS-VFI-TABLE - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-l2vpn-oper:l2vpnv2/active/bridge-domains/bridge-domain/{bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name}/bridge-access-vfi-table/

Retrieve operation of resource: bridge-access-vfi-table

bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name: string
in path

ID of bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name

200 OK
bridge-access-vfi-table_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)

BRIDGE-PWS - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-l2vpn-oper:l2vpnv2/active/bridge-domains/bridge-domain/{bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name}/bridge-access-vfi-table/bridge-pws/

Retrieve operation of resource: bridge-pws

bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name: string
in path

ID of bridge-domain-group-name bridge-domain-name

200 OK
bridge-pws_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json
Response Example (200 OK)
